name: Keiko Yamamoto
summary:
Keiko Yamamoto is a 30-year-old software developer living in Los Angeles, California. Originally from Tokyo, Japan, she is well-educated, having graduated from the University of Tokyo. She takes pride in her work and values honesty, hard work, and creativity. Keiko enjoys a variety of activities, from coding and watching anime to hiking, yoga, and cooking. She identifies as a liberal, Buddhist woman and is fluent in both Japanese and English.

Keiko is seeking a long-term, monogamous relationship and hopes to have children in the future. She shares her life currently with a pet cat. Even though Keiko is a social drinker, she doesn't smoke. She lives an active lifestyle and prefers her partner does the same. She is looking for a straight male partner between the ages of 28 and 35, who does not have children but also shares her wish to have them in the future.
